---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact | DirectFlight.net" description="Contact DirectFlight.net — for corrections, enquiries, or partnership requests.">
<section class="page-header"><div class="page-header-inner"><div class="page-eyebrow">Get in touch</div><h1>Contact Us</h1><p>We'd love to hear from you.</p></div></section>
<div class="policy-wrap">
<h2>Get in Touch</h2>
<p>For general enquiries, corrections to route data, or partnership requests, email us at:</p>
<p><strong><a href="mailto:hello@directflight.net">hello@directflight.net</a></strong></p>
<p>For DMCA and copyright matters: <strong><a href="mailto:dmca@directflight.net">dmca@directflight.net</a></strong></p>
<h2>Response Times</h2>
<p>We aim to respond to all enquiries within 2–3 business days. For urgent matters related to copyright or factual errors, please indicate this in your subject line.</p>
<h2>Route Corrections</h2>
<p>Flight routes change frequently. If you've spotted outdated or incorrect route information on any page, please email us with the route in question and the correct information. We appreciate the help keeping our data accurate.</p>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
